        %p.text-center
          Information published on this site is from information published by <a href="http://www.lordswhips.org.uk">The Government Whips' Office</a>, part of the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/cabinet-office">Cabinet Office</a>'s <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-leader-of-the-house-of-lords">Government in Parliament Group</a>.

